headline: ROLLINS, INC. ANNOUNCES REGULAR QUARTERLY CASH DIVIDEND
summary: Rollins, Inc. (NYSE:ROL), a premier global consumer and commercial services company, announced that the Board of Directors declared a regular quarterly cash dividend on its common stock of $0.165 per share payable September 10, 2025 to shareholders of record at the close of business on August 11, 2025.
